]</required_translations><script><![CDATA[/**
 * @param {params} params
 * @param {api} params.api
 * @param {TransformApiHelpers} params.helpers
 */
function evaluateProperty({
    api,
    helpers
}) {
    var records = api.data.get_all_account_contacts.results;
    if (records === undefined)
        return;
    const contacts = [];
    records.forEach(r => contacts.push({
        id: r._row_data.uniqueValue,
        label: r._row_data.displayValue
    }));

    return contacts;
}]]></script><script_api_version>2.0.0</script_api_version><sys_class_name>sys_ux_client_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2023-10-31 13:48:46</sys_created_on><sys_id>21a70fd447523110036bbce5536d43c2</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>typeahead_contact_items</sys_name><sys_package display_value="AT&amp;T Workspace" source="x_876519_att_work">e90c1d2e47c63110036bbce5536d43e6</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="AT&amp;T Workspace">e90c1d2e47c63110036bbce5536d43e6</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ux_client_script_21a70fd447523110036bbce5536d43c2</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2023-10-31 13:48:46</sys_updated_on><target>macroponent</target><type>transform</type></sys_ux_client_script></record_update>
